author: dirkv
msg: Fix bugs reported by Raj Kumar:
- The AclMethod is still allowing granting of privileges PRIVILEGE_READ_REVISION_METADATA,
PRIVILEGE_READ_REVISION_CONTENT which are not present in the privileges set returned by supported-privileges
- The aclmethod and the propfind methods still differ regarding their interpretation of the write privilege.
The aclmethod for write privilege does not seem to be granting/denying removeRevisionContent privilege in slide.
